creator: ScieNext
descriptionHtml:
Play when you want with all new music player. It's best music player loaded with some cool features you love to have in your perfect music player.
Use equalizer to customize your sound, create playlist, set sleep timer and play music with album, artist and all songs options. Support almost all audio formats.
It's one of the Best Offline Music player with some rich features to play music that is stored on your device


Features:
♪ Loaded with colorful and stylish themes
♪ Add a multiple or many songs to any playlist at once also add them to queue and play next.
♪ Use shuffle button to shuffle the songs.
♪ Edit music tags and album art
♪ Add to Favorite option to every song to add your favorites songs in inbuilt Favorites Playlist.
♪ Search music by tracks, album and artist.
♪ Set sleep timer
♪ Powerful bass Boost with virtualizer sound effect
♪ 5 band equalizer to customize sounds with 10 inbuilt presets.
♪ Create and manage playlist
♪ Add songs button in playlists
♪ Change order of songs in playlists
♪ Access recently added songs on your device
♪ Delete songs directly from player
♪ Refresh tracks on player using "refresh library" option.
♪ Sort songs as per your choice
♪ Notification control to control music player from notification bar
♪ Lock-screen widget to control music when screen is locked.
♪ Access music by folder browser
♪ Home screen widget supports
♪ Supports headset control

Available Languages
English, Portuguese(Brazil), Portuguese(Portugal), Spanish, French, German, Italian, Russian, Croatian, Turkish, Chinese, Arabic, Dutch(Netherlands), Romanian, Greek, Japanese, Danish

NOTE: This is not online music streaming player so you can't download or stream any songs using it. Search option is to find music that is stored on your device and not for finding songs online.

Feedback regarding music player is appreciated which can make it best audio player. we'd love to hear from you and we'll customize our player as per your valuable feedback.

Join us for regular updates:
